column5: I think you're supposed to meet a guy wearing a trench coat in the parking lot...he'll be wearing white socks as well.
Brian, just go to the counter, identify yourself and tell them that there's ticket(s) waiting for you from OFC.
JUST TELL HIM BUBBA SENT YA.He made then an offer they could'nt refuse
Yes.. will call window... sorry.. ive been busy!!
You better check into that boss. No tickets were there. They did give me and lew a ticket each though without a list of names.

T.J. I am planning on attending tomorrow with the tickets won here on OFC. Should I be prepared to 'buy' tickets??  Brian, Was it a big deal/hassle actually getting the free tickets??  Pls & Thx, Simon
No Simon. Once Lew started the tears,it was easy.  Seriuosly,they were nice.We waited for 5 minutes or so and they just gave us tickets and made us sign our names.
Thx for the reply Brian. Appreciate it. I'll make my son-in-law cry like a baby if I have to.
